<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.2.2">
<l>ceṟuntiṇ timilē ṟuṭaiya piṉṉai</l>
<l>peṟuntaṇ kōlam peṟṟā rūrpōl</l>
<l>naṟuntaṇ tīntē ṉuṇṭa vaṇṭu</l>
<l>kuṟiñci pāṭuṅ kūṭa lūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kūṭalūr, where bees which sip fresh nectar,</l>
<l>Fragrant and sweet, hum kuriñci [love] songs,</l>
<l>It seems, is the city of him who attained the fresh beauty of Piṉṉai,</l>
<l>Which was worthy [of him], [she] who had murderous, strong, humped bulls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
